---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Press" description="Press kit, assets, and contact.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold">Press</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">Everything journalists and analysts need.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold">Quick facts</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Open-source project by Милош Васић. No commercial entity operates a hosted Service yet.</li>
      <li>License: Apache-2.0 (code), CC-BY-SA-4.0 (documentation).</li>
      <li>Source: <a href="https://github.com/HelixDevelopment/HelixGitpx" class="text-primary hover:underline">github.com/HelixDevelopment/HelixGitpx</a> (mirrored to GitLab, GitFlic, GitVerse).</li>
      <li>GA tag: <code>v1.0.0</code>.</li>
      <li>12 Git provider adapters shipped.</li>
      <li>Active-passive multi-region recipe (EU-central / EU-west) — deployment artefact only; not an operator.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold">Boilerplate</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
      <em>HelixGitpx is a federated Git proxy that mirrors repositories
      across every major Git hosting provider. Teams push once;
      HelixGitpx replicates to GitHub, GitLab, Gitea, Gitee, Bitbucket,
      GitFlic, GitVerse, Azure DevOps, AWS CodeCommit, Forgejo,
      SourceHut, and any generic Git-over-HTTPS host. Policy-driven,
      AI-assisted, open source.</em>
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold">Assets</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Logos: <a href="/press/helixgitpx-logos.zip" class="text-primary hover:underline">helixgitpx-logos.zip</a> (SVG, PNG, 1×/2× dark/light).</li>
      <li>Founder headshots: on request.</li>
      <li>Product screenshots: on request.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold">Contact</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700"><a href="mailto:press@helixgitpx.io" class="text-primary hover:underline">press@helixgitpx.io</a> — response within 1 business day.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
